Monitors Sphinx, an open-source SQL full-text search engine (http://www.sphinxsearch.com/) for the following metrics by looking at the searchd logs:

* Queries per-minute
* Average query time 
* Average time per rebuild
* Index rebuilds
* Average results returned

Note that the first run will not return any data.

----

Created by Sam Sinensky (http://github.com/samsinensky) at Code and Beats (http://codeandbeats.com/) 12/29/09